The paper discusses the search and retrieval of multimedia objects, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of human feedback patterns and mental evaluation suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The exploration of the search space also implies a consideration of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
